title: Self- control plane- 8 cabines
short_description: Children are always interested in fun games and attractions. This attraction is designed for children, consists of 8 cabins and has a total capacity of 16 people. Operating at 380V, this attraction has a height of 6.5 meters and a diameter of 11.5 meters. The volume diameter of the attraction is 9 meters and the power is 11.5 kW.
short_description_uz: Bolalar doimo ko'ngilochar o'yinlar va attraksionlarga qiziqishadi. Ushbu attraksion bolalar uchun mo'ljallangan bo'lib 8 kabinadan iborat va umumiy sig'imi 16 kishini tashkil etadi. 380V kuchlanishda ishlovchi ushbu atraksion 6.5 metr balandlikka ega va 11.5 metr diametrda harakat qilish imkoniyatiga ega. Atraksionning hajm diametri 9 metrni tashkil etadi va quvvati 11.5 kW.

Этот аттракцион, работающий от напряжения 380 В, имеет высоту 6,5 метра и диаметр 11,5 метра. Объемный диаметр аттракциона – 9 метров, мощность – 11,5 кВт.
